ResourceHeader.ResourceName: ACE Electron Proton Alpha Monitor (EPAM) LEFS60 MFSA, Solar Wind Frame, Sectored Proton Fluxes, Daily Averages
ResourceHeader.Description: Daily-averaged sectored proton fluxes from the MF Spectrum Analyzer of the ACE/EPAM LEFS60 instrument. All energies thresholds take into account the incident particle type, shielding, and inactive dead-layer of the solid state detector. All fluxes are background corrected and are in the solar wind rest frame.
ResourceHeader.Acknowledgement: Thomas P. Armstrong, Fundamental Technologies LLC

InformationURL.Name: Explanation of EPAM print-groups and CSV file nomenclature.
InformationURL.Description: The Explanation HTML page at Fundamental Technologies describes how the numeric data from the ACE EPAM instrument are divided into different print-groups, the nomenclature of the ASCII-based comma-separated variable (CSV) files, and how those files can be accessed.

AccessURL.Name: ACE EPAM Daily-Averaged
AccessURL.Description: Parent directory containing the Daily-averaged fluxes for the ACE/EPAM instrument for the entire mission.

AccessInformation.Acknowledgement: Thomas P. Armstrong, Fundamental Technologies LLC

Parameter.Name: Time for the record
